title: Garbo Cafe und Kneipe im Cinema
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Located in the art house cinema. Most of the meals are vegetarian or vegan and are clearly marked. Drinks include coffee, tea and many juices which are fair trade and organic, plus the food is mainly organic. Online menu in English and Dutch.
